{"tid":1804051,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"宣傳自已的小說 黑暗騎士浩劫","createTime":"2019-12-30T16:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T14:03:35.000Z","uid":178311,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cc985b6987cacfe13f916d59681dc42315eaf3dd","tid":1804051,"uid":178311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:28:39.000Z","msg":"呢度係第二個更新地方，有興致就噤入去下面個網址睇啦。同埋講下有詳改善的地方。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/48405/黑暗騎士浩劫\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F48405%2F%E9%BB%91%E6%9A%97%E9%A8%8E%E5%A3%AB%E6%B5%A9%E5%8A%AB&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJv5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=e540019d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/48405/黑暗騎士浩劫</a>"},{"pid":"1b179aab24b1b0743c6ee3aee3f478754547dd21","tid":1804051,"uid":282118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T15:11:41.000Z","msg":"QQ？<br />\n可唔可以香港啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有支那味有啲難頂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qziMSg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qziMSg.jpg&h=e3966684&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4206de676a6f7591348be4336b9115f4db7f433","tid":1804051,"uid":178311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b179aab24b1b0743c6ee3aee3f478754547dd21","tid":1804051,"uid":282118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T15:11:41.000Z","msg":"QQ？<br />\n可唔可以香港啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有支那味有啲難頂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qziMSg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qziMSg.jpg&h=e3966684&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"已經改咗"},{"pid":"ad2299ea0515d5c0d445ddeed4e81d527a87c7c8","tid":1804051,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T18:13:02.000Z","msg":"有幾on9先會改自己仔但名做浩劫"},{"pid":"7a78a8